    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This power unit utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis retains its structural integrity, benefiting from M-specific aluminum suspension components and a carbon fiber roof to minimize the center of gravity. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the replacement of rod bearings with treated shells and new throttle actuators to ensure the VANOS system operates flawlessly. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. While the aesthetics show honest patina, the hydraulic steering rack and EDC-equipped dampers provide the precise feedback expected of a true driver\u2019s machine.",
