    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a wonderful balance of performance and pride of ownership. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, showing only the minor, inevitable stone chips on the lower front valance consistent with careful highway use. All body panels are straight with factory-spec gaps. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the leather upholstery is supple and free of cracks, though the driver\u2019s side bolster shows the light, natural softening of quality hide. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. I have maintained a rigorous service schedule, with the most recent oil service and multi-point inspection completed just last month. The engine idles smoothly and pulls with consistent power, while the transmission provides seamless shifts across all gears. It sits on a set of premium tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This has been a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle, and it comes with a complete set of owner's manuals and two sets of keys. It is a solid, honest car ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
